name: Ipé - Tree of Life III
description:
3/8

There where the rivers are the veins of the ground,
the breeze carries life and joy along.
There where the sun doesn't give truce,
and there's always a shadow to shelter you.

There where the Lapacho glows,
its shine will remind you pure gold.
If you find it, do not rush.
Take a breath,  take a nap.
